Report a Lost Card
TO REPORT A LOST OR STOLEN ATM/VISA Debit Card
Call 215-579-3400, Monday-Friday from 8:30 a.m. – 5 p.m.
After business hours, call 800-236-2442.
Traveling? Let us know.
Inform us of your travel plans, so your FNB ATM/VISA Debit Card will remain active and not be restricted by security.
Email us at EFT@fnbn.com. Please provide only your name, travel dates and destination. No account or card numbers are necessary.
Bank Routing Number
ABA Routing Number: 0319 1278 5
